node.title: Missing man in Christchurch found
node.description: A man who had not returned home since morning bike ride in Christchurch has now been found safe and well, police say.
node.content:
["A man who had not returned home since morning bike ride in Christchurch has now been found safe and well, police say.", "The man was found by a member of the public in Tai Tapu and is now on his way home to his family.", "", "
Murray Bennett, 67. Photo: Supplied / NZ Police
", "Police said Murray Bennett, 67, left his home in Hillsborough shortly after 11am but had not returned as expected.", "Police said he was found by a member of the public in Tai Tapu and was now on his way home to his family."]
